      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The engine starts and runs consistently, and the transmission is functional, though shifts may not feel as crisp as a newer model. The exterior has some noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and carpets. It is a solid, functional car that would benefit from some minor maintenance and cosmetic attention to bring it back to its best.",
